value.0: I cannot help you.
Hello I see you are a fellow student of the Arcane Arts.
Would you care to test yourself in a little challenge I made for fellow casters?

I have traveled far and wide and seen many things while learning the art spell weaving. I made this challenge to let people that have not seen as much as myself experience the world and test themselves.
I have 5 tasks that can not be done with physical prowess. Only those practiced at magic will be able to complete it.

What!?!?!?! The sense of adventure isn't enough for you? What about the thrill of taking on a challenger and defeating them? The fun of the game? What more could you want from such a proposition as mine?

You disappoint me I thought those of the arcane arts were different. I see now that my eyes were veiled. However if this is how you must have it..........I see you carry a stone that holds some of your magic in it.
Well your motives for actions may be impurw. However that deed itself was good and so if you can complete my challenge I will improve that rock for you.
I will make it usable at any time combat or not.
Very well I shall teleport you into my challenge. Good Luck.
I see you have defeated Dave. No small feat for the fighter but I found him easy to control with magic also.
Next you must prove you can evade attacks and run away when you are outmatched.
Yes all you have to do is stay alive for 60 seconds and you will have passed my challenge.
Nothing like a game of Tag, eh?

*Evil Grin* During my travels I was challenged to a game of tag by a fat gnome and so I accepted. When we got to where we were going to play tag, the gnome said meet my player and she came out. I was as amazed as you were by her speed and power.
I said I would pay her much more then he did. I told her to play tag with anyone that my appear in her room.
I placed a spell on her once she gets into "tag" mode she has one minute before my spell makes her feint.
You must fight in ranged combat. Are you ready?
Well played, Sir.
Yes and I am glad you are enjoying my challenge.
The Fourth Task is a way to test your skill at combat when your skill at magic is useless.
Don't worry I will give you a dagger to use it isn't that hard.
See now that wasn't as bad as you thought, was it?
Just think only one more task left and you have completed my challenge.
You get to fight the clone I made of myself...in a lesser form of course as there is no way you could defeat me in arcane combat.
I say so. Are you ready for the final fight?
You have defeated my clone and the challenge. For that I congratulate you.
Your most welcome. So as to fulfill my promise to you....let me see your magic stone and I will upgrade it.
I see my challenge has made you less of an adventurer. I my heart is filled with joy at this. May I at least port you back to the Entrance?
Finished here is your stone back and now I will port you back to the Entrance.
You have proven yourself.  There is nothing more I can do for you.
Yes I am.
Can you tell me more about this challenge?
OK and in this challenge you want me to do what?
If I do complete it. Do I get anything?
Well frankly Magnus, I am an adventurer. I don't do these for fun I do them to make a living. If I can't make a living off of it, I need to get something that will help me complete future quests.
What this buffitis rock? Yeah I got it from a farmer after I saved his kid from an evil witch.
Improve it how?
That would not help me make a living and so I must refuse your challenge. Good day to you sir.
OK...Then I accept your challenge.
No...Thank you for the offer however I do not feel up to challenge right now.
Why not I am always looking to test myself.
Thank you.
Yes he was kind of a push over....so you said something about 5 parts what are the other 4?
So.....I am suppose to just evade the monster?
Give me a second to get ready.
Sounds easy. Port me in.
HOLY ****, where did you find that thing?
So....how did you get her in this challenge?
Well she is a pro...what killed her?
Good thing without that she would have killed me. Anyway whats up next?
No
Yes
Thank you. You really have traveled far and wide for this collection haven't you?
I am.....so whats up next?
WHAT?!?! That is my only weapon what am I suppose to do with that?
No wait hold on.....
.....That sucked but I guess as I did it.......I can't complain to much.
Speaking of that task what is it.
If you say so.
Give me a min.
Lets do this.
Thanks
Nah I just wanted to see the challenge but thanks for your offer.
Very well. Thanks.
OK here ya go.
OK thanks.
